OL,5, John Riccitiello has resigned as chief 
OL,6, executive of game development tool     
OL,7, Unity following a controversial pricing
OL,8, change which angered gamers and        
OL,9, developers alike.                      
OL,11,FThe firm wanted to charge studios every
OL,12,Ftime a person installed a game using   
OL,13,FUnity's code which powers thousands of 
OL,14,Fmodern video games.                    
OL,16,FBig developers already pay a licensing 
OL,17,Ffee to use Unity in their games.       
OL,19,FThe company has since rolled back most 
OL,20,Fof its plans and apologised.           
